  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Saving Abandoned &amp; Homeless Elderly</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">It is our responsibility to care for those who once cared for us. The problem of abandonment of elderly is increasing daily and the elderly if not rescued eventually die on streets. We rescue abandoned and destitute elderly from the streets suffering from various physical and mental disabilities and provide them food, clothing, accommodation, medical facilities such as Physiotherapy, Regular Check-up and medication, Pathology Lab, X-ray and a lot of love, care and support and rehabilitate them.</narrative>
  </description>
